data.description: This 1,880 sqft Rambler Ranch-style gem boasts 3 beds, 2 baths, a spacious kitchen, and a master suite with a lavish ensuite bathroom, custom tile work, a generous walk-in closet, and solid surface stone countertops adding elegance to every corner. Step outside to admire the landscaping and a crescent driveway with ample parking, which wraps around, adding grandeur to your home's entrance.  The vast RV area accommodates all your toys with full hookups. A backup generator and propane supply add peace of mind. Clearwood is not just a home; it's a lifestyle. Enjoy miles of trails, a swimming pool, parks, and three lakes in the community. Clearwood defines perfection, where elegance and adventure harmonize beautifully.
